        <h1 class="project-title">Composition &amp; Form Studies</h1>
        <p class="project-meta">2025</p>
      </header>
      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">Overview</h2>
        <p>Studies focused on composition through reduction, contrast, and spatial relationships.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">Tools</h2>
        <p>Gouache</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">Process</h2>
        <p>Compositions were developed by simplifying real-world forms into geometric structures, focusing on the interaction between positive and negative space. High-contrast black and white was used to emphasize balance, rhythm, and hierarchy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">Reflections</h2>
        <p>Strengthened my understanding of composition as foundational — how space, rather than form alone, defines visual structure.</p>
      </div>
