        <h2 class="section-label">Process</h2>
        <p>Garments were designed conceptually, then translated into AI-generated visuals through a structured ComfyUI pipeline. A LoRA-based workflow maintained stylistic consistency across models, outfits, and environments. Outputs were sequenced into a runway-style video, with poster designs extending the project into editorial format.</p>
